    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <description
  >Unified template registry for onboarding communications (Email/SMS/In-App) with channel-specific template IDs and message bodies. Templates are synced from Salesforce Email Templates (for Email) and can reference Twilio Messaging Templates (for SMS). All fields are read-only and synced nightly via EmailTemplateSyncService or manually. Example: A Communication_Template__c with Communication_Type__c=&quot;Email&quot; and Email_Template_Id__c=&quot;00X000000000123&quot; might be used by a Follow_Up_Rule__mdt to send reminder emails when onboarding requirements are incomplete. Templates are linked to Vendor Programs via Vendor_Program_Recipient_Group__c associations.</description>
